Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:02.54,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a shooting comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:06.52,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan's logic works wonders on\Nhearts exhausted by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:10.19,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's hints are crabs and a whale!\NUnexpected things look like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.36,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:16.89,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:02:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tastes great! Can't have summer without beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! You shouldn't just drink! You need to eat a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Don't be so naggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:13.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I was all excited when he said it was a fancy hotel dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:16.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but it's nothing but light snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:20.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who takes kids to beer gardens to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:27.73,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Dentist\NKeigo Endo (33)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:37.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That man's at a beer garden but hasn't even had a sip...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you drunk already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bathrooms aren't that way! Really, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Endo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes. I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is the deal off?! I got the money and didn't tell the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Let me hear Keita again! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:40.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did this man—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old man! Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:04:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't say it out loud,\Nbut I think there was a kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you said, there's a good chance they're holding him for ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It sounds like he hasn't contacted the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Driver. Try not to lose the taxi in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:33.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Endo Dental Clinic"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:52.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Closed for today."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dentist, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to talk with him first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we don't know where the kidnapper is looking from,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it could be a neighbor behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a good idea! I'll be a patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My tooth hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Dad's going to talk to the dentist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I can't hold on! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.39,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to bother you on your day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My kid's tooth hurts and he won't shut up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:48.84,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Understood. Please come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:05:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come into the examination room...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon my late introduction. I am Detective Kogoro Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro Mouri? That famous detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} heard my phone conversation—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Could you tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the kid's right, then I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright. This may be some sort of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you said, my son was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Keita.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I let him play by himself in the front yard this afternoon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:57.80,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Keita! Let's go to the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Keita?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:08.81,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Took the kid. Call the police and he's dead. Wait for a call."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's written on ordinary copy paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what did the kidnapper tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a young man's voice on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told me to put 30 million yen in used bills in a briefcase
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and to be at Starlight Hotel's beer garden at 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But a little after 6:00, he called me\Nand canceled the exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he explain why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. All he said was that he would call again tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the kidnapper was suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He probably never intended to get the money tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:01.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He likely watched Endo{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} from somewhere in the beer garden
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:05.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}to make sure he hadn't contacted the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you got the first call,\Ndid you hear Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I asked the kidnapper to put him on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} seem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sounded unexpectedly cheerful; he didn't seem afraid at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is odd. You would expect him\Nto at least miss his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She died of a disease last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that's why Keita grew fond of his kindergarten teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the women in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. Now I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kidnapper is likely working with a woman good with children,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and she's taking care of Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:57.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The old man might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:09:04.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Meaning we can't rest easy,\Nbut it's unlikely they'll hurt Keita{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. I think you probably should call the police now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the kidnappers will be caught if the police intervene!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what guarantee do I have\NKeita will return unharmed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are my only hope now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please! Help bring Keita back unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well! I was the one who came to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's work together to somehow solve this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we can't stay here too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll leave for tonight and talk on the phone from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:09:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:04.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll need to borrow this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about. I will return Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right! I appreciate your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:20.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I attached the transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:23.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now we just wait for the kidnappers to call!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri Detective Agency...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They called?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did they say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They demanded 20 million more, and gave me two hours to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I had them put him on just like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he said something odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:57.18,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:11:00.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Keita! Is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.26,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.79,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Keita! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:05.39,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah! There's lots of crabs here, Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.30,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Crabs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:07.96,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:11.20,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Listen! Call the cops and—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.93,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A whale! A whale is spouting bubbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:17.13,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Loudmouthed brat! I'll contact you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.17,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:22.17,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello?! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:25.51,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Loudmouthed? The kidnapper said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood. You get the money ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With any luck, I'll have Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} back within two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?! Please do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! You have a clue about the kidnappers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is by lots of crabs and a bubble-spouting whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crabs and a whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it's the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:12:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be dumb! Whales only spout air deep underwater!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a real whale that Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} saw.\NIt was probably a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A model?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that would be at the aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:12.98,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Southern Aquarium
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have any whale models?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. We do have various kinds of\Ncrabs, but no whale models...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! Must be a different aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have no time! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say... Are you sure the crabs have to be real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said there were lots of crabs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the kidnapper said,\N"What are you talking about?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean the kidnapper couldn't see any?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they didn't call from the aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at that, Dad! It's a whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:06.24,Signs,,0,0,0,,"Nichiuri TV"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! Nichiuri TV's mascot is a whale this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that be what Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} saw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so, then he was where that blimp was visible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it! The blimp was above Beika Park\Nwhen the kidnappers called!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday's deal was at a hotel in Beika Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go back and look for a place in Beika Town with lots of crabs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has to be somewhere near there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any luck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! Our time's up!\NThe kidnappers might've called.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:42.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They called two minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They told him to stand at the end of Platform 1 in Karajuku Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Karajuku Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You keep looking for the crabs, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:15:00.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even if they did lose to the kidnappers, my transmitter's on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:03.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I {\i1}will{\i0} find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:11.11,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Karajuku Station
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think they'll be on a train?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll probably exchange the money elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Throw the money here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you care about the kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. But Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} got the license plate number on film.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll know his identity soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:20.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's staying in the same spot. Their hideout should be nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:30.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Almost there! Just around that corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! They must've changed briefcases here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the old man got the license plate number, so we can still—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was this the kidnapper's?! Was that license plate a fake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:57.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no! Now that they have the money,\Nthey might kill Keita{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:03.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Find where there's lots of crabs and where the whale blimp was visible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:09.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Didn't he say the whale was spouting air bubbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That blimp wasn't spouting anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:19.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What does it mean? Was it not the blimp he saw?! Or maybe—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:44.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can't see it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:45.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:49.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It might be visible from that Starlight Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:13.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Beika Park. And then that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:16.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Keita{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} saw the smoke from that waste incineration facility...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:30.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It would look like that only where the park and the tower line up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:34.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:39.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But this is too low. It needs to be the same altitude as the blimp
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:41.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}to make it look like it's spouting air.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could they be in this hotel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:50.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:56.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The tables and chairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:59.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could the crabs actually be—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There they are! The crabs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:29.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The tables and chairs look like crabs from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:34.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No doubt about it! Keita{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} is in some room in this hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know which room this boy is staying in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's in a room one floor down. But he just left with his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:01.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Alright! I found you! Keita{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} is still unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yaiba Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Joker! Hiyaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:13.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yaiba Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are we really going to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quit asking and stop worrying about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two are kidnappers! Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! Nobody move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:37.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move and he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get over there! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is there anything to kick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bike's right out front!\NRun like hell once we're out the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keita! I'm so glad you're all right! Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Daddy, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:23:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know they were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just dumb luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was looking for the crabs when I found Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.34,0:23:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I shouted that it was a kidnapping,\Nthey rushed to get away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.38,0:23:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and wound up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brought it upon themselves, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.82,0:23:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector Megure{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-dono{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} explained everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you contact us when you learned it was a kidnapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't trust me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.91,0:23:40.78,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}For the next hour, Inspector Megure gave the old man a good scolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:42.84,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Not that that's a bad thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a homicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.97,0:23:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be possible to leave from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:24:01.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why is there a bloodstain here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.35,0:24:06.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ikuta{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} was standing here in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:08.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.15,0:24:15.16,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.16,0:24:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-N-N-N-Next Conan's Hint: Cigarettes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.46,0:24:22.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, it's another surprising, well-executed trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.50,0:24:24.63,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Can you see crows in the dark of night?
